    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不是闭环，我的意思是流程到Serverless结束。不过你提醒了我，最后那个节点可以保留作为终态标识，让E指向自己表示Serverless是最终交付形态。前面A到D是逐步演进的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解成五个节点：A(K8sCluster)、B(ServiceMesh)、C(HelmChart)、D(Serverless)、E(Serverless终态)，其中A→B→C→D→E，且E自环。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
